Studying about threat actors, attack vectors, insider or outsiders threats.

a threat actor individual or entity that is driving the attack.
insider/internal threats are from inside the organisation/company.
outsiders threats are outside from the organinsation/company.

threat actors could be new or advanced.

What is their motivation/intent?

Another country/state attacking is an advanced persistent threat. 

Shadow IT - an invididual in organistaiton asking IT for wifi or something. 
Got service on their own implenting something that's unauthorised.

Threat actors are looking for common attack vectors to get into the organisations. 
Common attack vectors could be physical, digital, human. 

